creator: Point Pick-Up Technologies, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
"With GigPoint you’ll be able to:

- Earn points for every successful order you complete

- Redeem these points for useful rewards

- Open a zero-monthly fee bank account with no overdraft fees, auto-bill paying with no extra fees and a free debit card.
Future banking services will include direct deposit from your Point Pickup Stripe account, cash advances, etc.

- Purchase comprehensive health insurance packages at a very competitive rate"
